<br>
Alot of parnaoia and selfishness. Don't let that guy come cuz he may cut into our loot. <br>
<br>
What a load of bunk. Learn MY rule kids, thats the golden rule. You do as you should, you do as expected. You take responsibility for your actions, for your words, for your raids. YOu share. You help others. And you quit being so goddamn selfish.<br>
